This website uses [Google Analytics](http://www.google.com/analytics/), a web analysis service provided by Google Inc (“Google”). Google Analytics uses so-called [cookies](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HTTP_cookie), text files, which are stored on the computer of a website visitor. These cookies collect anonymous traffic data and allow for an analysis of the visitor’s usage of this website.

For more information, please read:

1. [Google Analytics Terms of Service](http://www.google.com/analytics/tos.html)
1. [Google Privacy Policy](http://www.google.com/privacy.html)

